          To take differential selection into account, we relax
          the assumption of the intra-strand <ENAMEX TYPE="ORGANIZATION">Chargaff</ENAMEX>'s rule as
          follows. The <NUMEX TYPE="CARDINAL">four</NUMEX>-parameter model presented above
